ic) the quotient horospheric\nlamination is minimal: each horosphere is dense.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 May 2006 17:59:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Nov 2006 12:20:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2010 12:47:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-02-11"}
