ity properties of quasiconjugations of the circle.\nThis, together with the congruence relations leads to the result that the\nsubset of maximal representations is always real semialgebraic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 May 2006 23:00:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Oct 2006 10:03:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 15 Sep 2008 11:41:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-09-15"}
